    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor 24 Piece Deluxe Gold Panning Kit with Sluice Box was designed to give you the edge while panning for gold with portability in mind; inside the backpack, we&#039;ve included our 50&quot; Aluminum Folding Sluice Box. This lightweight, sluice box for gold panning incorporates traditional tried and true design aspects in an elongated 50 inch run out. What makes this unit different and extra handy is the ability to fold up to just 15 inches tall by 12 inches wide, easily fitting into a 5 gallon bucket as well as the included 30L canvas backpack making this ideal for beginner gold panning, day hikers, adventurers, and seasoned miner 49ers</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 5lb Genuine Gemstone Paydirt Kids Dig Kit (4 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Excitement and discovery await with this ASR Outdoor Complete 14pc Kids Gemstone Paydirt Dig Kit!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>GEMSTONE PAYDIRT:</strong> Enjoy the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones! Each five pound bag is packed with a rich assortment of genuine rough gemstones, two pounds worth, as well a small assortment of tumbled stones, all waiting to be discovered!</li>\n    <li><strong>TOP QUALITY GEMSTONES:</strong> In your paydirt, you’ll uncover an assortment of rough gemstones like Amazonite, Amethyst, Carnelian, Citrine, Fuchsite, Fluorite, Labradorite, Pyrite, Rainbow Moonstone, Strawberry Quartz, Sea Jasper, Smoky Quartz, Tiger Eye and more</li>\n    <li><strong>SCIENCE KIT:</strong> A great hands on learning activity for kids, little budding geologists will love sifting through paydirt to discover all the different gemstones! Double sided gemstone identification chart and gemstone facts sheet makes identifying gemstones easy and fun</li>\n    <li><strong>HOW TO USE:</strong> Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen, dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no gemstones were missed</li>\n    <li><strong>KIT INCLUDES:</strong> 5lb rough gemstone paydirt bag, 8x12 burlap bag, screening instructions card, gemstone identification chart, collapsible bucket, sifting screen, scoop, two 4x6 drawstring burlap bags, magnifying loupe, tweezers, microfiber cloth and safety goggles</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/70392/8qyfLENh5W4HXF6ck1kmxQeIRgGsKj-metaNWxibWFkX21haW4uanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"Excitement and discovery await with this ASR Outdoor Complete 14pc Kids Gemstone Paydirt Dig Kit\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 5LBGEMKITPARENT</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This kit includes all the equipment you need for successful gemstone paydirt processing: Each five pound rough gemstone paydirt bag is a treasure trove waiting to be uncovered! Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine rough gemstones, and a small assortment of tumbled stones, unleash the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying found precious gemstones. In your gemstone paydirt bag, you’ll discover an assortment of rough gemstones like Amazonite, Rough Amethyst, Carnelian, Citrine, Clear Quartz, Fuchsite, Labradorite, Pyrite, Moonstone, Rose Quartz, Sea Jasper, Smoky Quartz, Tiger Eye and more!</p>\n  <p>This geology science kit is a great hands on learning activity for kids; little budding geologists will love sifting through paydirt to discover all the different gemstones! Double sided gemstone identification chart and gemstone facts sheet makes identifying gemstones easy and fun for all ages!</p>\n  <p>Whether you&#039;re a seasoned gemstone enthusiast or curious beginner, our 14pc complete gemstone paydirt kit delivers the thrill of sifting through organic material to uncover authentic rough gemstones. Perfect for hobbyists, gemstone collectors or kids and families looking for a fun, hands on and engaging learning activity.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Outdoor 24 Piece Deluxe Gold Panning Kit with Sluice Box was designed to give you the edge while panning for gold with portability in mind; inside the backpack, we've included our 50\" Aluminum Folding Sluice Box. This lightweight, sluice box for gold panning incorporates traditional tried and true design aspects in an elongated 50 inch run out. What makes this unit different and extra handy is the ability to fold up to just 15 inches tall by 12 inches wide, easily fitting into a 5 gallon bucket as well as the included 30L canvas backpack making this ideal for beginner gold panning, day hikers, adventurers, and seasoned miner 49ers.",
